  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐπραξία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐπραξία\"><span data-text=\"Εὐπραξία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Εὐπραξία\">[Ε]ὐπραξ̣[ία]</span></span></span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡρακλεί\n                    δαι Ἡρακλείδα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡρακλεί\n                    δαι\"><span data-text=\"Ἡρακλεί\n                    δαι\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἡρακλείδα\">Ἡ̣ρ̣α̣κλε[ί-]<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>δαι</span></span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδα\"><span data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδα\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἡρακλείδα\">Ἡρα[κ]λείδα</span></span></span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ἐποίη̣[σε]</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Εὐπραξία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Εὐπραξία\">Εὐπραξία</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδαι\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἡρακλείδα\">Ἡρακλείδαι</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδα\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἡρακλείδα\">Ἡρακλείδα</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐποίησε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ἐποίησε</span>  <span dir=\"ltr\">(vac.)</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐπραξία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐπραξία\"><span data-text=\"Εὐπραξία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Εὐπραξία\">[.]ΥΠΡΑ.[..]</span></span></span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡρακλεί\n                    δαι Ἡρακλείδα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἡρακλεί\n                    δαι\"><span data-text=\"Ἡρακλεί\n                    δαι\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἡρακλείδα\">...ΚΛΕ[.]<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΔΑΙ</span></span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδα\"><span data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδα\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἡρακλείδα\">ΗΡΑ[.]ΛΕΙΔΑ</span></span></span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙ.[..]</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Εὐπραξία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Εὐπραξία\">ΕΥΠΡΑΞΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδαι\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Ἡρακλείδα\">ΗΡΑΚΛΕΙΔΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"Ἡρακλείδα\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"Ἡρακλείδα\">ΗΡΑΚΛΕΙΔΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησε\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΕ</span> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003476_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003476_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003476.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003476-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after Manganaro, controlled against photograph</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Manganaro: Εὐπραξ[ία] Ἡρακλεί</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"2\">2: <span>Manganaro: δαι Ἡρακλείδα</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"3\">3: <span>Manganaro ἐποίησε</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Eupraxia made (this) for Herakleidas son of Herakleidas</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The irregularity of the layout may suggest later recutting of the block. Manganaro's reading appears optimistic when compared against the photograph.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 49.1276 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1999 41 no. 15 fig. 92 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001813</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Large wide and square letters, regularly set out, without notable serifs. Alpha has broken bar; epsilon has shorter middle bar; kappa has short arms; omicron is slightly smaller than other letters and above the line; pi has equal length vertical strokes and slight overlap of the horizontal; rho has a small closed loop</p> Line 1-3  40-45  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
